    <bug_when>2013-04-30 14:30:25 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>With the following input XML the JSoup parser produces a DOM that contains trailing spaces under the body element that span two TextNodes.

bc. &lt;html&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\ntext\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html

The WhitespaceCleanupProcessor makes the assumption that trailing (and leading) spaces are contained within a single TextNode and thus does not strip them correctly in this scenario.</thetext>
